description:
online collaboration platform for those shaping the future

WECHANGE is the cooperative online collaboration platform for all who will shape the future together. More than 35,000 people are connected on wechange.de, working together on online documents, coordinate appointments, manage shared files, and more.

WECHANGE is Open Source, meets highest data protection requirements, and is hosted on servers in Germany, driven by 100% CO2 neutral eco power. The WECHANGE communityware is also deployed as white-label solution for organisations, cities and communities.
